            <p style="margin-top: 10px; font-size: 0.75rem; opacity: 0.75;">Quality ratings based on data accuracy, coverage depth, update frequency, and user reviews. Cost indicators: $ = Under $5K/year, $$ = $5K-$25K, $$$ = $25K-$100K, $$$$ = $100K+</p>
